    "+300k multi-word typos (2-3 errors per query, realistic multi-token)",
    "+120k question-style queries (where/how/which/is-it-worth-it)",
    "+120k comparison/alternatives (A vs B, alternatives to X)",
    "+150k long-tail composed queries (qualifier+color+modifier+category)"
